{"tid":1469621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:05:52.000Z","uid":140738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fba9bbfad1beee2d8953c46449e7ec0fc4d36db6","tid":1469621,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:27:14.000Z","msg":"民間記者會可以諗下：<br />\n<br />\n既然警察已經講到明有臥底，<br />\n<br />\n我地就應該假設我地每次行動都有人扮示威者，<br />\n<br />\n而之前警黑合作已經有先例，<br />\n<br />\n咁亦都可以假設黑社會都會扮示威者。<br />\n<br />\n而且公安、武警、解放軍都有機會會做臥底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點係<br />\n<br />\n明顯今晚機場就有人扮示威者然後做啲過激行為，<br />\n<br />\n因為有啲行為就唔係平時示威者會做嘅野，<br />\n<br />\n好似first aid單野咁<br />\n<br />\n亦都可以將一啲今晚過左火嘅行為推落班臥底到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個已經唔係割唔割席嘅問題，<br />\n<br />\n個問題係啲鬼做左啲離譜嘅野，<br />\n<br />\n其實唔係我地嘅問題，<br />\n<br />\n咁我地做咩要討論割唔割席呢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有個問題係，<br />\n<br />\n班鬼一定會走出黎做好多dirty works，<br />\n<br />\n到時我地又係咪一句不割席就攬哂所有野。"},{"pid":"5b1c9c11a74864c4ccf10a53bbc2ef6db1b1255a","tid":1469621,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"024ee6c592676194f65484a207ab64aacea13043","tid":1469621,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484247c5f5e3219ceb0002cd0298233a76d1782c","tid":1469621,"uid":11515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"對付禁制令絕招：示威者喬裝成旅客<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bdb02ad0d4d0569c8298d06950e152ea9c8dfa72","tid":1469621,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9790479ad937fe38c8cafc5e86c22bb5f7256bf","tid":14